      "title": "一、概率基础回顾: 从随机变量到概率分布 - 示例 1",
      "code": "import numpy as np\n\n# 生成样本数据\nnp.random.seed(42)\nX = np.random.normal(loc=5, scale=2, size=1000)  # 均值5, 标准差2\nY = 3 * X + np.random.normal(loc=0, scale=1, size=1000)  # Y与X线性相关\n\n# 计算均值\nmean_X = np.mean(X)\nmean_Y = np.mean(Y)\nprint(f\"均值: X={mean_X:.3f}, Y={mean_Y:.3f}\")\n\n# 计算方差\nvar_X = np.var(X, ddof=1)  # 样本方差，ddof=1表示无偏估计\nvar_Y = np.var(Y, ddof=1)\nprint(f\"方差: X={var_X:.3f}, Y={var_Y:.3f}\")\n\n# 计算协方差矩阵\ncov_matrix = np.cov(X, Y, ddof=1)\nprint(f\"协方差矩阵:\\n{cov_matrix}\")\nprint(f\"协方差 Cov(X,Y)={cov_matrix[0,1]:.3f}\")\n\n# 计算相关系数\ncorr = np.corrcoef(X, Y)[0,1]\nprint(f\"相关系数: {corr:.3f}\")\n\n# 多维数据的协方差矩阵\ndata = np.random.multivariate_normal(mean=[0, 1, 2], cov=[[1, 0.5, 0.2],\n                                                          [0.5, 2, 0.3],\n                                                          [0.2, 0.3, 3]], size=500)\ncov_multi = np.cov(data, rowvar=False)  # 每列是一个变量\nprint(f\"多维协方差矩阵形状: {cov_multi.shape}\")\nprint(f\"对角线(方差): {np.diag(cov_multi)}\")",
