      "title": "三、最大似然估计 (MLE) 与最大后验估计 (MAP) - 示例 1",
      "code": "import numpy as np\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n\n# 生成真实数据\ntrue_mu, true_sigma = 3.0, 1.5\ndata = np.random.normal(true_mu, true_sigma, size=1000)\n\n# MLE 估计\nmu_mle = np.mean(data)\nsigma_sq_mle = np.var(data, ddof=0)  # 有偏方差\nsigma_mle = np.sqrt(sigma_sq_mle)\n\nprint(f\"真实参数: μ={true_mu}, σ={true_sigma}\")\nprint(f\"MLE估计: μ̂={mu_mle:.4f}, σ̂²={sigma_sq_mle:.4f}, σ̂={sigma_mle:.4f}\")\n\n# 验证：绘制似然函数曲面\nmu_range = np.linspace(2, 4, 100)\nsigma_range = np.linspace(1, 2.5, 100)\nMu, Sigma = np.meshgrid(mu_range, sigma_range)\nlog_likelihood = np.zeros_like(Mu)\nfor i in range(len(mu_range)):\n    for j in range(len(sigma_range)):\n        mu_try = mu_range[i]\n        sigma_try = sigma_range[j]\n        log_likelihood[j,i] = np.sum(np.log(np.exp(-(data-mu_try)**2/(2*sigma_try**2)) \n                                            / np.sqrt(2*np.pi*sigma_try**2)))\n# 找到网格上的最大值\nmax_idx = np.unravel_index(np.argmax(log_likelihood), log_likelihood.shape)\nprint(f\"网格搜索MLE: μ̂={mu_range[max_idx[1]]:.4f}, σ̂={sigma_range[max_idx[0]]:.4f}\")\n\n# 对比无偏方差\nsigma_sq_unbiased = np.var(data, ddof=1)\nprint(f\"无偏方差估计: {sigma_sq_unbiased:.4f}\")",
      "language": "python",
      "repo": "None",
      "install_cmd": "pip install numpy pandas"
