      "code": "# 这是一个伪代码示例，演示如何调用VLM API为图表生成描述\n# 实际运行需要API密钥和网络请求\n\nimport requests\nimport base64\n\ndef generate_vlm_description(image_path, api_key):\n    \"\"\"\n    使用VLM (如GPT-4V) 为图像生成描述。\n    \n    Args:\n        image_path: 图像文件路径\n        api_key: API密钥\n    \n    Returns:\n        description: 生成的文本描述\n    \"\"\"\n    # 1. 读取图像并编码为Base64\n    with open(image_path, \"rb\") as image_file:\n        base64_image = base64.b64encode(image_file.read()).decode('utf-8')\n    \n    # 2. 构造API请求\n    headers = {\n        \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\",\n        \"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {api_key}\"\n    }\n    \n    payload = {\n        \"model\": \"gpt-4-vision-preview\",\n        \"messages\": [\n            {\n                \"role\": \"user\",\n                \"content\": [\n                    {\n                        \"type\": \"text\",\n                        \"text\": \"请详细描述这张图片中的图表内容，包括标题、坐标轴、趋势和关键数据点。\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"type\": \"image_url\",\n                        \"image_url\": {\n                            \"url\": f\"data:image/jpeg;base64,{base64_image}\"\n                        }\n                    }\n                ]\n            }\n        ],\n        \"max_tokens\": 300\n    }\n    \n    # 3. 发送请求（实际运行需取消注释）\n    # response = requests.post(\"https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions\", \n    #                           headers=headers, json=payload)\n    # description = response.json()['choices'][0]['message']['content']\n    \n    # 模拟返回\n    description = \"这是一张2023年各季度营收的柱状图。标题为'2023 Quarterly Revenue'。X轴为Q1, Q2, Q3, Q4。Y轴为营收（百万美元）。数据点：Q1: 100, Q2: 120, Q3: 150, Q4: 180。整体呈现持续增长趋势。\"\n    \n    return description\n\n# 假设我们有一个图表图片\n# desc = generate_vlm_description(\"chart.png\", \"your-api-key\")\n# print(desc)\nprint(\"VLM描述生成示例（模拟结果）：\")\nprint(generate_vlm_description(\"dummy_path.png\", \"fake_key\"))",
