      "title": "代码示例 4",
      "code": "import numpy as np\nfrom PIL import Image\nimport io\n\ndef compute_visual_similarity(image1_path, image2_path):\n    \"\"\"\n    计算两张图片的视觉相似度（使用简单的特征哈希）。\n    实际应用中应使用CLIP等模型。\n\n    Args:\n        image1_path: 第一张图片路径\n        image2_path: 第二张图片路径\n\n    Returns:\n        similarity: 0-1之间的相似度分数\n    \"\"\"\n    # 模拟：实际应使用预训练模型提取特征\n    # from sentence_transformers import SentenceTransformer\n    # model = SentenceTransformer('clip-ViT-B-32')\n    #\n    # img1 = Image.open(image1_path)\n    # img2 = Image.open(image2_path)\n    #\n    # emb1 = model.encode(img1)\n    # emb2 = model.encode(img2)\n    #\n    # similarity = np.dot(emb1, emb2) / (np.linalg.norm(emb1) * np.linalg.norm(emb2))\n\n    # 模拟随机特征\n    np.random.seed(42)\n    emb1 = np.random.randn(512)\n    emb2 = np.random.randn(512)\n\n    similarity = np.dot(emb1, emb2) / (np.linalg.norm(emb1) * np.linalg.norm(emb2))\n\n    return similarity\n\n# 使用示例\nsim = compute_visual_similarity(\"chart1.png\", \"chart2.png\")\nprint(f\"视觉相似度: {sim:.4f}\")\n\n# 模拟两个相同图片\nemb_same = np.random.randn(512)\nsim_same = np.dot(emb_same, emb_same) / (np.linalg.norm(emb_same) * np.linalg.norm(emb_same))\nprint(f\"与自身相似度: {sim_same:.4f}\")",
